{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"a041a996a2","title":"右派言论——反对反右派鬥争","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"309223a703","index":0,"year":1957,"month":6,"day":null,"articleId":"a041a996a2"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"21870b49ca","name":"刘剑明"},{"id":"4a296ee343","name":"吴见鑫"},{"id":"67b01672c7","name":"湖北医学院"},{"id":"7fbc63ec39","name":"孔麒"},{"id":"c3540497b9","name":"许道诚"},{"id":"cabdeb85ba","name":"曹作炎"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"f2cd662ac9","type":"title","text":"右派言论——反对反右派斗争","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a041a996a2"},{"id":"a09e2b0b80","type":"authors","text":"湖北医学院吴见鑫许道诚孔麒曹作炎刘剑明","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a041a996a2"},{"id":"c80a8a2945","type":"paragraph","text":"“党的反右斗争，不符合党整风原则，妨碍整风运动进行。”（湖北医学院　吴见鑫）","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a041a996a2"},{"id":"d96536cc5a","type":"paragraph","text":"“谁说我是右派分子，我就打死他；谁说我落后，就凑死他。”（湖北医学院　许道诚）","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a041a996a2"},{"id":"9a5342be92","type":"paragraph","text":"“整风六大标准发表的太迟了，知识分子在运动中无一定的尺度，因而在鸣放中出现一些错误。”（湖北医学院  孔麒）","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a041a996a2"},{"id":"e043dfa2d8","type":"paragraph","text":"“右派分子的形成，是‘三害’的必然结果。”（湖北医学院　曹作炎）","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a041a996a2"},{"id":"fc2bc8d793","type":"paragraph","text":"“在鸣放斗争，由于我们揭开的错误太多了，受不了，所以来反右斗争。”","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a041a996a2"},{"id":"abe1de3d9f","type":"paragraph","text":"“党不愿意整风，党不虚心接受人民的意见。把整风的矛头对准民盟。” （湖北医学院  刘剑明）","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a041a996a2"},{"id":"69e9a77e12","type":"paragraph","text":"“又把工人、农民搞起来了（指工农起来反击右派——原编者注）；工人农民这些大老粗晓得什么？”（湖北医学院  李建群）","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a041a996a2"},{"id":"549f3a8030","type":"paragraph","text":" 来源：《高等学校右派言论选编》（中共中国人民大学委员会，1958年8月）。","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a041a996a2"}],"page":{"id":"5e61139774","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a041a996a2","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}